aid; amount.</catchline><para>Except as provided in sections 79-1008.02 to
79-1010, each local system shall receive equalization aid in the amount that
the total formula need of each local system, as determined pursuant to sections
79-1007.01 to 79-1007.23 and
section 79-1007.25, exceeds its total formula resources as determined
pursuant to sections 79-1015.01 to 79-1018.01.</para>
